{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8939874624","title":"七律·到韶山","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"eade9db1d9","index":0,"year":1959,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"8939874624"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"b54677064c","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"韶山在湖南省湘潭县，是毛泽东的故乡。1927年1月，毛泽东在湖南考察农民运动时曾回到韶山。三个月以后，蒋介石发动了四一二反革命政变，随后5月21日湖南军阀许克祥在长沙袭击省总工会、省农民协会等革命团体，居杀革命群众，这就是马日事变（旧时用韵目代日期，马日即21日）。当时韶山成立了农民自卫军，拿着枪和梭镍，准备配合其他农民武装力量进攻长沙。后来反动军队大举进攻韶山，农民自卫军在英勇抵抗后失败。毛泽东在1959年6月25日至27日重返韶山，离1927年1月已经32年多。这首诗便是对于32年来的斗争和胜利的概括。"},{"id":"bc2c378ac0","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"别梦依稀究逝川，久别重归，又唤起了已依稀如梦的斗争和失败的回忆。"},{"id":"dc087f2ef6","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"载，古代的一种刺杀武器。4]黑手高悬霸主鞭，黑手，反革命的血程魔掌。霸主，指蒋介石。本句和领联出句，是写那个时期的阶级斗争。"},{"id":"682403bad0","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"救，豆类的总称。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e4ca9a2d33","type":"title","text":"七律·到韶山口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"b54677064c","type":"paragraph","text":"1959年6月25日到韶山。离别这个地方已有32周年了","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"bc2c378ac0","type":"paragraph","text":"别梦依稀咒逝川，回","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"dc087f2ef6","type":"paragraph","text":"故园三十二年前。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"682403bad0","type":"paragraph","text":"红旗卷起农奴就则，","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"ddcc787b93","type":"paragraph","text":"黑手高悬霸主鞭。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"ac956a5a36","type":"paragraph","text":"为有辆性多壮志，","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"788e7fd86a","type":"paragraph","text":"敢教日月换新天。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"7c828b9f4c","type":"paragraph","text":"喜看稻救千重浪，","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"3c4ca3412b","type":"paragraph","text":"遍地英雄下夕烟。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"},{"id":"89c2fd629b","type":"paragraph","text":"里达人货《伟人故里》（诗意画）","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624"}],"page":{"id":"0dae7992d7","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"8939874624","start":151,"end":152}}}},"__N_SSG":true}